Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.12,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:11.63,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had this feeling ever since last night \Nthat I'm supposed to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:17.15,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, my shoes and bag sure feel heavy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:17.99,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This house...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:23.17,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow ended up walking to\NRohan-sensei's house without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:30.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,The door's open...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:34.05,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to stop by and \Nthank him for yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:38.85,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,but then I'd be late for school.\NIt's probably a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He might still be asleep, \Nsince he's a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:44.70,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't just barge into his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bad idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.94,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He's working so frantically.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:02.33,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:06.36,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shake the feeling that\Nbeing here is actually terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:07.85,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:09.69,JoJo-main,rohan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:10.96,JoJo-main,Rohan,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:12.71,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.71,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.34,JoJo-main,Rohan,0000,0000,0000,,However, could I ask you \Nto wait a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.86,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Two more pages, and I'll be done \Nwith the manuscript for next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.93,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll be done in about twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:28.25,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just say he'd finish \Ntwo pages in twenty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:29.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hear him wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Two totally blank pages of\Nmanuscript in twenty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,No way... And he said next week's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:39.83,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,We only just read this week's manuscript \Nyesterday, and he'd just finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.75,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're not going to do pencils first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.77,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.86,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even draw that \Ncomplicated story in pencil first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:06.52,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting more and more complete... \NAnd he's even drawing the backgrounds with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.17,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:22.62,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really see it. What did he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:29.08,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,What?! H-He's doing the beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.85,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He's flinging ink around like shurikens,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.54,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,and hitting exactly the right spots \Nwithout going out of the lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.23,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:39.30,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to fill in beta \Nby hand with a brush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.05,sign_3860_44_Boom,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Boom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.56,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He's already done with the beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:48.29,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been about two minutes \Nsince the page was completely white!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.56,JoJo-main,Rohan,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.95,JoJo-main,Rohan,0000,0000,0000,,The urge to work keeps welling up in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.84,JoJo-main,Rohan,0000,0000,0000,,I want to draw so bad, I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.22,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to keep drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.24,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've been able
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to draw nineteen pages in one night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.34,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drawing a masterpiece right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.79,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Your experiences are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:11.29,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm using your experience \Nas the source of my story, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.58,JoJo-top,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.29,JoJo-top,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.23,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! I want your next reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.84,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your next page!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.33,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,The more pages I take, \Nthe more weight you'll lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.76,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't care, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:30.96,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're going to become \Na masterpiece and live forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.05,sign_5117_63_Flip,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Flip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.42,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:41.99,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.66,JoJo-MainTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo's Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.66,JoJo-MainTitle2,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond is Unbreakable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:03.34,JoJo-MainTitle3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,556)}Jojo's Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:03.34,JoJo-MainTitle4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,556)}Diamond is Unbreakable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.67,JoJo-top,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:05:01.35,JoJo-EpTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(572,605)}Episode 15{\fs20}  Let's Go to the Manga Artist's House, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.36,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,I've managed to make a book
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.05,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,from a single panel rather \Nthan an entire work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.36,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm growing as a manga \Nartist and as a Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.41,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going read this now, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.51,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:23.26,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those faces belong to Shining \NDiamond's Josuke Higashikata
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.22,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and The Hand's Okuyasu Nijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.38,JoJo-main,Oha,0000,0000,0000,,How curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.60,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Why would those two be at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.07,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Koichi would \Ntell those two about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.14,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.65,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.81,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Josuke and Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:47.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how they found \Nout I was here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.29,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now they can save me somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.53,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:06:00.25,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get them to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:05.59,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okuyasu and Josuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.20,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.39,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:17.04,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I don't have any \Ninterest in Josuke and Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.82,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to finish up the \Nlast two pages for next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:24.23,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and steal even more material from Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.94,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:30.34,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You were watching a \Nmanga artist do his work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.45,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,This is where that manga artist works?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.93,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan Kishibe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.50,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Is he famous or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.79,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of him, Josuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.42,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Even that bastard Hazamada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.31,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,made fun of me for not\Nknowing what {\i1}Perman{\i0} was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:49.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't what I wanted \Nto say to them just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.51,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,But what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:54.36,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were following you \Nbecause we were worried
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,since you were just wandering around,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:07:00.19,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,but if nothing's wrong, then good. I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.39,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.76,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come inside \Nand watch with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.52,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:08.58,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd get nervous around somebody famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.80,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.26,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just satisfied knowing that you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.20,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't come here to meet some chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.03,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:17.85,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.18,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:27.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I forgot to tell them \Nsomething really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.22,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.26,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was going to ask for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.50,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke! Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.19,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head to school soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.06,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.54,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.73,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.23,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:49.64,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I wanted to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.68,sign_22633_306_Can_Not,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,I can not attack the manga \Nartist, Rohan Kishibe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.99,sign_22633_306_Can_Not,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,can not
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:56.45,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! I can't ask them for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.32,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can there be a Stand as terrifying as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:06.25,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Door is way too strong! \NThere's no way to attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.84,sign_11659_136_Scribble_Scribbl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Scribble Scribble Scribble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.20,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:18.06,sign_11811_139_Scribble_Scribbl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Scribble Scribble Scribble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:17.62,JoJo-internal/narrator,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he's going to rip \Neverything out of me and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.97,sign_11942_140_Stop,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.81,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming into this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.78,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do downstairs just now, Koichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.59,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.42,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.52,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there! Don't you dare turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:43.18,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Try anything funny, and I'll crush \Nyou with my Stand, you little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.49,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:49.21,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you knew that \NI was in danger, but I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:53.08,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he figured it out coincidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.93,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized, but the wound on your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.48,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,must have signaled him \Nthat something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.88,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you scratched it or \Ncaught it on something while crawling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:06.51,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was so absorbed, I didn't even notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.22,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you figured it out, \Nright, Okuyasu Nijimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.18,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand name: The Hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.55,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,You have a complex regarding\Nyour dead brother, Keicho,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and whenever you try to make a decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:23.08,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you wish that your brother were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:24.98,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.96,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.59,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koichi, tell me what \Nthis guy's Stand is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.46,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.58,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say anything that'll put \NRohan Kishibe at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,If you see even one panel, you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:44.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.59,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at that manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.81,JoJo-main,Okku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I told you not to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.25,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu, I wasn't interested in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that you're in \Nthis house, I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.82,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to turn you into material, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.29,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.30,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.33,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.92,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.02,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.55,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke Higashikata,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.00,JoJo-main,Rooha,0000,0000,0000,,you're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:29.65,JoJo-Eyecatch3,Signtop,0000,0000,0000,,Ro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:29.85,JoJo-Eyecatch3,Signtop,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.10,JoJo-Eyecatch3,Signtop,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan Kishi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.06,JoJo-Eyecatch3,Signtop,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan Kishibe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:30.69,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Hea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:30.73,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Heave
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:30.81,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:30.85,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:30.98,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:31.06,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Doo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.06,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Signbot,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Door
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.76,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.70,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is up with this manga artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.96,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:45.11,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Koichi, \NI have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.83,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.21,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think Josuke Higashikata
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is hiding behind that door there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.25,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't he come out, Koichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:03.08,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke is hiding so he won't see your manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:06.60,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is correct. You're pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:11.63,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu Nijimura there didn't \Nknow about my Heaven's Door,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.43,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was able to trick him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:19.49,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, because of that, Josuke \NHigashikata now knows who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.32,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,On that point, I feel I'm seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:25.48,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,no, without a doubt, put at \Na very big disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:30.83,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,There's also another reason that Josuke \NHigashikata is hiding behind the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.08,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.63,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent that from happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.63,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I have to somehow drag him \Nout from behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:45.35,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the middle of trying to figure \Nout how he's going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.85,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,That's also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.64,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not the exact answer I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.56,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,The correct answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:57.77,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke Higashikata is contemplating whether
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,he should flee this mansion alone or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.20,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke would never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.01,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:09.60,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,It was written in your files that \NJosuke Higashikata's personality
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,would never allow him to abandon you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:16.61,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, manga artists \Nhave a habit of thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:20.21,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,every conceivable possibility \Nbecause of their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.41,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Like, what are all of the possible actions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.02,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that the protagonist can \Ntake in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:31.05,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, having Josuke run away \Nnow that he knows who I really am
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:33.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is truly troublesome to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.64,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Run... Actually, that might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.31,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be able to get Jotaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and if Yukako finds out \Nwhat's happening to Koichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll be super pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.65,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! We could win with her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.91,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't want to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.01,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, Josuke! Hurry up and let them know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.20,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I explained that to you \Nso that it wouldn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.89,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Okuyasu! I already wrote that into your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:57.92,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:02.92,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow you to explain what I wrote \Nin there to those two, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:07.64,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.26,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What's written there, Koichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.27,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.86,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,We can't run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.89,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:22.86,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what's written there, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.36,sign_19250_244_If_Josuke_Higash,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,If Josuke Higashikata makes\Ntrouble for Rohan Kishibe,\NI will commit suicide\Nby self-immolation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.11,sign_19286_245_If_Josuke_Higash,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,If Josuke Higashikata makes\Ntrouble for Rohan Kishibe,\NI will commit suicide\Nby self-immolation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.33,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,S-Suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:35.83,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll commit suicide if \NJosuke even tries to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.21,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey! I'll commit \Nsuicide by self-immolation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.84,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! Like I'd die \Nin such a horrific way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.22,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.77,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,But you will! He's invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:53.13,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't defy him, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.56,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! My right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.87,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:07.77,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that he came out, \Nbut he was basically dragged out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:13.62,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... That's rather childish and simple, \Nbut it might be quite effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.51,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,This room is small and \Nthere's nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.58,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,If you can defeat me in a single blow, \NHeaven's Door will disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Okuyasu won't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.25,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:29.25,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Closing his eyes is pretty simple, \Nbut it might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:32.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he doesn't see the manuscript, \NHeaven's Door is powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Just come charging straight in like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.27,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:40.42,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to open your eyes somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.34,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He was able to withstand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.47,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.95,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,If he comes charging at me, I'll be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:55.75,JoJo-topinternal,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a protagonist in a manga, \Nwhat would I do in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:58.71,sign_21386_269_seconds,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.94,JoJo-topinternal,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,How would I get him to open his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.46,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.84,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.16,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:06.67,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something written in Koichi's file...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.36,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,There! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.95,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to laugh at your hairstyle, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:18.82,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,That's from, like, twenty or thirty years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.87,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think that's cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.65,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.36,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he gets angry if I say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:31.92,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of hard to believe, \Nbut the file doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.20,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100% true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:40.01,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.83,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,J-Josuke, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.46,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and say that one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.84,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,You opened them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.25,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:54.03,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you think \Nthat hairstyle is cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't look good on you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.61,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,It's lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:04.28,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Though a dirty little bird might \Nlike to make your head its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.48,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a maybe, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.90,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.99,JoJo-internal/narrator,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.60,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:23.75,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.56,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:40.56,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know that I opened his eyes \Nand showed him the manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.53,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.22,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that I showed it to him... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:57.28,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did you fly off to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:00.74,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Come back out here, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.75,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,No, he totally didn't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.18,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:08.05,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean that he's so worked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.56,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't even know what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.50,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you hiding, you dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.84,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.67,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He's the kind of guy that loses sight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:23.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of everything, even that manuscript, \Nwhen someone disses his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.93,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea he actually got this mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.90,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,This is way worse than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.89,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:42.95,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something about Josuke's personality \Nthat Koichi didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.17,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,That means it's information \Nthat's not in the file!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:50.80,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why does he get so \Nmad about his hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:54.34,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a reason... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.35,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who disses my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:18:00.43,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't keep quiet, no matter who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.88,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,The reason behind his hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:05.02,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I heard a little about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.61,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,That just might be why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.61,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:13.82,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It has to do with when \NJosuke was a kid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:19.17,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,This story is going to include my own
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:21.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,guesses about why this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.04,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, when Josuke was four,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,he passed out from an \Ninexplicable high fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:33.39,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,and for fifty days, they weren't\Nsure whether he'd live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.39,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.49,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He found out later that it \Nwas right around the time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.36,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when Jotaro and Mr. Joestar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:47.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,went to Egypt to defeat the man named DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.36,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time, they had \Nno idea it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:54.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so Josuke's mom drove him \Nto a hospital in S City.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:59.49,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,But on that day, Morioh was hit with \Nits worst blizzard in 18 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.91,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.92,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,Cars don't come by here often,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.60,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,and there are no pay phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.20,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,I should have called an \Nambulance at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:17.82,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have brought \NJosuke out in this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.96,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:31.31,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you want? Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.19,sign_28201_345_That_kid_is_sick,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,That kid is sick, right?\NI'll push your car for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.45,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:51.04,sign_28201_345_That_kid_is_sick,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and\Nstep on the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:56.42,sign_28590_348_Once_you_get_goi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get moving,\Ndon't stop. Just keep going... \NOr your tires will get stuck in the snow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.11,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.23,JoJo-flashback,Tomo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.08,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,His mom looked for that boy later,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but couldn't find a single lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:37.96,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Though the boy didn't personally\Nsave Josuke's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.35,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,the four-year-old Josuke \Nthought that what the boy did
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.23,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,made him his hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.53,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He's an inspiration that's \Nburned into his heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and his example of how to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.84,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,So when someone insults that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.56,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,something deep in his heart snaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.04,JoJo-flashback,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:01.06,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,but I admire him so much \Nthat I copied his hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:04.65,JoJo-flashback,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't forgive anyone who insults it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:07.63,JoJo-flashback,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,because it's the same as insulting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.69,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,I think that story might be the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.61,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Though I thought Josuke was making it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:16.19,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wasn't listening very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.79,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... I had no idea something \Nlike that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.63,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan's holding a pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:25.06,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! You're going to try again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.26,JoJo-main,Roh,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:30.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wanted to sketch this and write\Na memo before I lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:36.21,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful story! And I just \Nexperienced something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.52,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get to experience \Nsomething like this often.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:42.40,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,If I can make it work in my own project...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.97,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:47.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I moved to Morioh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.26,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until he dies, he'll keep trying \Nto use anything as material
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for his manga, no matter how \Nhorrible the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:56.61,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, you have to commend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:22:01.67,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Putting good and bad aside, \NI have to admire that attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.28,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a super manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:07.30,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, manga artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.95,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done punching you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:14.18,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,You sort of have to commend him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.81,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
